OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784017089
OL,3,CHomes evacuated as fire crews tackle
OL,4,Cblaze at caravan park
OL,6,FWatch: Plumes of smoke could be seen
OL,7,Ffor miles after fire engulfs caravan
OL,8,Fpark (credit: Richie Addison)
OL,10,FMore than 125 firefighters have been
OL,11,Ftackling a blaze in Oxfordshire that
OL,12,Fswept through a caravan park and
OL,13,Fsurrounding fields.
OL,15,FThe alarm was raised on Sunday
OL,16,Fafternoon at Oaks caravan park in
OL,17,FFyfield Wick near Kingston Bagpuize.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
