OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784017089
OL,3,CHomes evacuated as fire crews tackle
OL,4,Cblaze at caravan park
OL,6,FAt its height there were fourteen fire
OL,7,Fcrews, seven specialist vehicles and
OL,8,Fadditional officers from across
OL,9,FOxfordshire, supported by
OL,10,FDWFireRescue, Royal Berkshire Fire and
OL,11,FRescue Service and Buckinghamshire
OL,12,FFire & Rescue Service were tackling
OL,13,Fthe fire.
OL,15,FThe site has been evacuated and there
OL,16,Fare no reported injuries from the fire.
OL,18,FPlumes of smoke could be seen for
OL,19,Fmiles, with nearby residents urged to
OL,20,Fclose their windows and doors.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
