OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784017089
OL,3,CHomes evacuated as fire crews tackle
OL,4,Cblaze at caravan park
OL,6,FThose that have had to leave their
OL,7,Fhomes have been taken to a nearby
OL,8,Fsports ground.
OL,10,FThey are being supported by Thames
OL,11,FValley Police, Oxfordshire County
OL,12,FCouncil Joint Oxfordshire Resilience
OL,13,FTeam, Rapid Relief Team UK, South &
OL,14,FVale district council and other local
OL,15,Forganisations.
OL,17,FMultiple fire crews remained overnight
OL,18,Fon Sunday - with a number of engines
OL,19,Fremaining at the scene on Monday
OL,20,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
