OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784017089
OL,3,CHomes evacuated as fire crews tackle
OL,4,Cblaze at caravan park
OL,6,FThe cause is currently considered
OL,7,Faccidental however inspectors will
OL,8,Fcontinue their investigatio today.
OL,10,FFire Control staff from the joint
OL,11,FThames Valley Fire Control Service say
OL,12,Fthey have spent the past twelve hours
OL,13,Fco-ordinating a 'significant' movement
OL,14,Fof resources, as services deal with
OL,15,Fmultiple other incidents across the
OL,16,FThames Valley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
